commit message: Don't set network alarm if there's no network connection.

Reworked location parsing.

Location parsing is much more generic now, handling any message with a
properly formatted geo: string.

This works for OSMAnd and Orux Maps and might work for others.

Align with upstream emoji System.

TODO: Filter emojis not available on the current Android platform.

Merge remote-tracking branch 'upstream/master' into merge_3.6.1
